{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-index-tsx","path":"/posts/Language/HTML/01_HTML.md/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"65e64671-309d-5ad5-84b6-0e191307d4fb","html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-web\">1. Web</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#11-components-of-a-web-page\">1.1. Components of a Web Page</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#12-browser\">1.2. Browser</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-html\">2. HTML</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#21-element\">2.1. Element</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#211-global-attributes\">2.1.1. Global Attributes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#212-semantic-tags\">2.1.2. Semantic Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#213-inline--block-tags\">2.1.3. Inline &#x26; Block Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#214-similar-tags\">2.1.4. Similar Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#215-form-and-input\">2.1.5. &#x3C;form> and &#x3C;input></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"1-web\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-web\" aria-label=\"1 web permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Web</h1>\n<p><strong>the collection of web pages linked each other through links</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"11-components-of-a-web-page\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-components-of-a-web-page\" aria-label=\"11 components of a web page permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.1. Components of a Web Page</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>HTML</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>The basic structure of a web page</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>CSS</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>The layout and design of a web page</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>JavaScript</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Running a web page dynamically</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"12-browser\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#12-browser\" aria-label=\"12 browser permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.2. Browser</h2>\n<p><strong>Simply speaking, the software that drives the code on a webpage</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"2-html\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-html\" aria-label=\"2 html permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. HTML</h1>\n<p><strong>Hyper Text Markup Language</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hyper Text</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Hypertext is text which contains links to other texts.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Markup Language = Structured language</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>It is a language that specifies the structure of documents or data using v tags.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"21-element\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-element\" aria-label=\"21 element permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1. Element</h2>\n<p><strong>Element = Tag + Content.</strong> Each tag has its own attributes that provide additional information about the tag.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Tag</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>An HTML tag is a piece of markup language used to indicate the beginning and end of an HTML element in an HTML document.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Content</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>Information that tags have</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"211-global-attributes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#211-global-attributes\" aria-label=\"211 global attributes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1.1. Global Attributes</h3>\n<p><strong>The global attributes are attributes that can be used with all HTML elements.</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_standardattributes.asp\">HTML Global Attributes</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Attributes</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>class</td>\n<td>a list of classes that the element is in</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>data-*</td>\n<td>assign user-cumstom data which can be transmitted between HTML and DOM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hidden</td>\n<td>browser doesn't rendering the element</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>id</td>\n<td>unique(recommended) id of the element</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>style</td>\n<td>css code</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>tabindex</td>\n<td>give the order of accessibility with 'tab' key</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>title</td>\n<td>additonal explanation when mouse-curser is on</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>lang</td>\n<td>the language of the element's content (for accessibility)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"212-semantic-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#212-semantic-tags\" aria-label=\"212 semantic tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1.2. Semantic Tags</h3>\n<p><strong>A semantic element clearly describes its meaning to both the browser and the developer.</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/html/html5_semantic_elements.asp\">HTML Semantic Tags</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Attributes</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>header</td>\n<td>represents a container for introductory content or a set of navigational links.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>nav</td>\n<td>defines a set of navigation links.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>main</td>\n<td>Specifies the main content of a document.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>section</td>\n<td>defines a section in a document.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>article</td>\n<td>specifies independent, self-contained content.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>aside</td>\n<td>defines some content aside from the content it is placed in (like a sidebar).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>footer</td>\n<td>bdefines a footer for a document or section.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"213-inline--block-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#213-inline--block-tags\" aria-label=\"213 inline  block tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1.3. Inline &#x26; Block Tags</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Inline Tags</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>tag</th>\n<th>usage</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;a></code></td>\n<td>link to another url</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;b></code>, <code>&#x3C;strong></code></td>\n<td>bold</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;i></code>, <code>&#x3C;em></code></td>\n<td>italic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;br></code></td>\n<td>change the line</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;img></code></td>\n<td>image</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;span></code></td>\n<td>meaningless inline container</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Block tags</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>tag</th>\n<th>usage</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;p></code></td>\n<td>paragraph</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;hr></code></td>\n<td>a thematic break</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;ol></code>, <code>&#x3C;ul></code></td>\n<td>list</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;pre></code></td>\n<td>express html contents</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;blockquote></code></td>\n<td>long quote</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>&#x3C;div></code></td>\n<td>meaningless block container</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"214-similar-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#214-similar-tags\" aria-label=\"214 similar tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1.4. Similar Tags</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;i> vs &#x3C;em></code>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;i></code>: italic only visually</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;em></code>: italic with emphasis</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;b> vs &#x3C;strong></code>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;b></code>: bold only visually</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;strong></code>: bold with emphasis</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;ul> vs &#x3C;ol> vs &#x3C;dl></code>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#x3C;ul>-&#x3C;li></code>: unordered-list</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;ol>-&#x3C;li></code>: ordered-list</li>\n<li><code>&#x3C;dl>-&#x3C;dt>, &#x3C;dd></code>: definition-list</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"215-form-and-input\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#215-form-and-input\" aria-label=\"215 form and input permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1.5. &#x3C;form> and &#x3C;input></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>&#x3C;form></strong>\n<ul>\n<li>The &#x3C;form> tag is used to create an HTML form for user input. It can submit several input fields at once.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>&#x3C;input></strong>\n<ul>\n<li>The &#x3C;input> tag specifies an input field where the user can enter data.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Types</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>text</strong>: text</li>\n<li><strong>password</strong>: input is being hidden</li>\n<li><strong>email</strong>: email form</li>\n<li><strong>number</strong>: number</li>\n<li><strong>file</strong>: type of the available file can be determined by <code>accept</code> attribute</li>\n<li><strong>checkbox</strong>: checkbox</li>\n<li><strong>radio</strong>: only one can be chosen between the inputs that have the same <code>name</code> attribute</li>\n<li><strong>color</strong>: color picker</li>\n<li><strong>date</strong>: date picker</li>\n<li><strong>hidden</strong>: hidden from the user</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;form>\r\n  &#x3C;label for=\"agreement\">description of the input&#x3C;/label>\r\n  &#x3C;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"agreement\" id=\"agreement\" />\r\n  &#x3C;!-- 'for' attribute is linked to 'id' attribute -->\r\n  &#x3C;input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" />\r\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-web\">1. Web</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#11-components-of-a-web-page\">1.1. Components of a Web Page</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#12-browser\">1.2. Browser</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-html\">2. HTML</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#21-element\">2.1. Element</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#211-global-attributes\">2.1.1. Global Attributes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#212-semantic-tags\">2.1.2. Semantic Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#213-inline--block-tags\">2.1.3. Inline &#x26; Block Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#214-similar-tags\">2.1.4. Similar Tags</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#215-form-and-input\">2.1.5. &#x3C;form> and &#x3C;input></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"01. HTML","createdAt":"2022-11-08","updatedAt":"2022-12-28","tags":null,"description":null,"reference":null}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"id":"65e64671-309d-5ad5-84b6-0e191307d4fb","parent":{"id":"8a51e8d8-11c8-5ca0-8ac4-3b7003db9174","name":"01_HTML","relativePath":"Language/HTML/01_HTML.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"01. HTML","createdAt":"2022-11-08","updatedAt":"2022-12-28"},"excerpt":"1. Web 1.1. Components of a Web Page 1.2. Browser 2. HTML 2.1. Element 2.1.1. Global Attributes 2.1.2. Semantic Tags 2.1.3. Inline & Blockâ€¦"}]}},"pageContext":{"pagePath":"posts/Language/HTML/01_HTML.md","regex":"/^(?!.*README).*Language\\/HTML.*$/","relativeDirectory":"HTML","id":"65e64671-309d-5ad5-84b6-0e191307d4fb","parent":{"id":"8a51e8d8-11c8-5ca0-8ac4-3b7003db9174","name":"01_HTML","relativePath":"Language/HTML/01_HTML.md"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1484934524","2644037009","4059933791"],"slicesMap":{}}